-- Ziraat raises borrowing from European Investment Fund to 2.1 billion lira
-- By Ayla Jean Yackley
-- Wed Jul 23, 2014 02:10AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, July 23 (Reuters) - Turkey's state-run lender Ziraat said on Wednesday it had increased a loan from the European Investment Fund to 2.1 billion lira ($998 million) from a previous 1.3 billion lira.

